name: Prodigy Robolo
additionalNotes:
From Rocky Patel, comes a Best Cigar Prices exclusive, the Prodigy. Constructed with an oily Ecuadorian Habano wrapper and Habano binder, with fillers from both the Nicaragua and Honduras fields of Rocky Patel. This cigar carries a nice mellow spice throughout, and bring along notes of dark chocolate on the palate.

Strength: Medium-Full Bodied 
Origin: Nicaragua 
Wrapper: Habano 
Shape: Straight
